    <h3>ABOUT THIS SITE</h3>
    <p>Home Post explores military life and military families in San Diego. Blogger Beth Ford Roth was born into a military family, and has covered issues important to servicemembers and their loved ones for many years. She has worked as a broadcast journalist in both commercial television and public radio.</p>

